ors%20have%20proven%20so%20popular%20that%20Chinese%20firms%20have%20been%20willing%20to%20buy%20them%20through%20underground%20markets%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Finside-chinas-underground-market-high-end-nvidia-ai-chips-2023-06-19%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReuters%20reported%20in%20June%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20US%20export%20rules%20bar%20Nvidia%20from%20selling%20its%20top-end%20processors%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20preparing%20to%20report%20second-quarter%20earnings%20for%20its%20fiscal%20year%20after%20markets%20close%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20AI%20companies%20and%20investors%20set%20to%20watch%20closely%20to%20hear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-chipmaker-cofounder-ceo-wealth-net-worth-ai-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECEO%20Jensen%20Huang's%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20outlook%20for%20products%20vital%20to%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Nvidia's%20first%20quarter%2C%20where%20it%20announced%20a%20massive%2019%25%20jump%20in%20revenue%20to%20%247.2%20billion%20from%20the%20previous%20quarter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.nvidia.com%2Fnews%2Fpress-release-details%2F2023%2FNVIDIA-Announces-Financial-Results-for-First-Quarter-Fiscal-2024%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHuang%20said%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20increasing%20our%20supply%20to%20meet%20surging%20demand%26quot%3B%20for%20products%20like%20the%20H100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20outside%20regular%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-triple-production-h100-chips-ai-drives-demand-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A169