%20illustration.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e5d59e4c17ff0019bace6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20LinkedIn%20logo%20and%20the%20Chinese%20flag.%3Cp%3E%20Budrul%20Chukrut%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Chinese%20spy%20created%20several%20fake%20LinkedIn%20profiles%20to%20target%20UK%20officials%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20London%20reports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recruitment%20consultant%20was%20offered%20%2410%2C000%20each%20time%20to%20hand%20over%20details%20of%20an%20intelligence%20services%20candidate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnother%20Chinese%20agent%20previously%20confessed%20to%20using%20LinkedIn%20to%20find%20people%20likely%20to%20possess%20sensitive%20information.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Chinese%20spy%20has%20been%20using%20LinkedIn%20to%20try%20to%20get%20UK%20officials%20to%20hand%20over%20state%20secrets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2F1ba8f1bc-4102-11ee-8b31-3c9c533abb75%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20period%20of%20at%20least%20five%20years%2C%20the%20spy%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20working%20from%20the%20Chinese%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security's%20(MSS)%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%20%E2%80%93%20created%20several%20profiles%20using%20stock%20images%20as%20profile%20pictures%2C%20and%20sometimes%20listed%20fake%20companies%20as%20the%20employer%2C%20before%20approaching%20security%20officials%2C%20civil%20servants%2C%20and%20scientists%20who%20had%20access%20to%20sensitive%20information%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Times.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20security%20services%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20most%20prolific%20spy%20in%20a%20generation%20to%20work%20against%20British%20interests%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%20The%20spy's%20main%20alias%20was%20Robin%20Zhang%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20though%20the%20names%20%3Cspan%3EEric%20Chen%20Yixi%2C%20Robin%20Cao%2C%20Lincoln%20Lam%2C%20John%20Lee%2C%20and%20Eric%20Kim%20were%20also%20used.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spy's%20strategy%20involved%20building%20up%20relationships%20with%20people%20and%20then%20offering%20them%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20for%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recruitment%20consultant%20was%20offered%20%2410%2C000%20for%20every%20time%20they%20handed%20over%20details%20of%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20intelligence%20services%2C%20while%20other%20targets%20were%20told%20they%20could%20have%20free%20trips%20to%20China%20and%20lucrative%20conference%20appearances%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20security%20minister%20Tom%20Tugendhat%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Insider%20that%20the%20Home%20Office%20is%20aware%20of%20%3Cspan%3EChinese%20Intelligence%20using%20LinkedIn%20and%20other%20social%20media%20sites%20to%20target%20British%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20government%20employees%20who%20need%20to%20exercise%20caution%20%E2%80%93%20it's%20businesses%20with%20commercially%20sensitive%20information%2C%20as%20well%20as%20researchers%20and%20academics%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20taking%20action%20to%20disrupt%20and%20deter%20these%20threats.%20Our%20new%20National%20Security%20Act%20has%20put%20our%20espionage%20laws%20back%20on%20the%20front%20foot%2C%20and%20MI5%20are%20helping%20people%20understand%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20fake%20profiles%20used%20by%20foreign%20spies%20and%20other%20malicious%20actors%20through%20their%20Think%20Before%20You%20Link%20campaign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-agent-exploited-linkedins-relentless-algorit