is%20expected%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-completes-final-lunar-orbital-move-next-stop-moon-4312465%5C%22%3Ea%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon%20%3C%2Fa%3Etoday.%20The%20lander%20will%20touch%20down%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Moon%20at%20around%206%3A04%20PM%2C%20said%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20the%20ISRO's%20follow-up%20attempt%20after%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20faced%20challenges%20during%20its%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20in%202019%20and%20was%20eventually%20deemed%20to%20have%20failed%20its%20core%20mission%20objectives.%20India's%20first%20lunar%20mission%20was%20Chandrayaan-1%2C%20during%20which%C2%A0the%20satellite%20made%20more%20than%203400%20orbits%20around%20the%20moon%20and%20the%20mission%20was%20concluded%20when%20communication%20with%20the%20spacecraft%20was%20lost%20on%20August%2029%2C%202009%2C%20according%20to%20ISRO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.isro.gov.in%2FChandrayaan_1.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChandrayaan%252D1%26amp%3Btext%3DChandrayaan%252D1%252C%2520India%2527s%2520first%2520mission%2C2008%2520from%2520SDSC%2520SHAR%252C%2520Sriharikota.%5C%22%3E%20Chandrayaan-1%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20being%20assembled%2C%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20visited%20the%20ISRO%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-sci-tech%2F5-things-you-did-not-know-about-chandrayaan-other-moon-missions-8904492%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2011th%20President%20Of%20India%20back%20then%20asked%20the%20scientists%20about%20what%20evidence%20Chandrayaan-1%20will%20exhibit%20to%20prove%20that%20it%20had%20been%20to%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20scientists%20revealed%20that%20it%20would%20have%20pictures%20of%20the%20Moon's%20surface%2C%20the%20former%20President%20said%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20enough%2C%20the%20report%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20suggested%20that%20Chandrayaan-1%20should%20carry%20an%20instrument%20that%20could%20be%20dropped%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20this%20advice%20that%20the%20scientists%20at%20ISRO%20made%20design%20changes%20to%20Chandrayaan-1.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20reporters%20after%20seeing%20the%20first%20pictures%20of%20Earth%20taken%20by%20terrain%20mapping%20camera%20on%20board%20Chandrayaan-1%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fkalam-happy-with-moon-s-pics-42909%5C%22%3EAPJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20extremely%20happy%20after%20seeing%20the%20images%20and%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20Indian%20should%20be%20proud%20of%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia's%20third%20lunar%20mission%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%20by%20the%20LVM3%20rocket%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre.%20With%20the%20involvement%20of%20almost%201%2C000%20engineers%20and%20scientists%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-brains-behind-chandrayaan-3-4321182%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20in%20the%20making%20for%20four%20years%2C%20ISRO%20Chairman%20S%20Somanath%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EISRO%20has%20earlier%20informed%20that%20the%20propulsion%20module%20will%20continue%20to%20orbit%20the%20moon%2C%20even%20after%20the%20lander%20makes%20the%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692787140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Fv5pfbpe_apj-abdul-kalam-quotes_625x300_15_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-when-a-