l%20reason.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%20Phoenix%20workers%20have%20also%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20safety%20violations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Phoenix%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsummer-2023-heat-wave-tracker-temperature-records-2023-5%5C%22%3Erecord-breaking%3C%2Fa%3E%20summer%20heat%20isn't%20the%20only%20thing%20on%20the%20rise.%20Tensions%20are%20boiling%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20of%20the%20world's%20leading%20chipmaker%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-taiwan-semiconductor-phoenix-arizona-factory-chipmaker-job-qualification-debate-2023-8%5C%22%3ETaiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Co%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20current%20workers%20said%20operational%20mismanagement%20and%20administrative%20chaos%20have%20delayed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftsmc-delays-start-of-chip-production-in-arizona-plant-1032465900%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20of%20the%20chip%20factory%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20not%20the%20reasons%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-phoenix-chip-semiconductor-factory-biden-global-economy-china-taiwan-2022-12%5C%22%3ETSMC%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20TSMC%20said%20the%20opening%20would%20likely%20be%20pushed%20back%20a%20year%2C%20until%202025%2C%20partly%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-jobs-taiwan-semiconductor-chip-worker-skills-work-ethic-2023-8%5C%22%3Ea%20lack%20of%20skills%20and%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20US%20workers.%20To%20get%20things%20back%20on%20track%2C%20the%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20visas%20for%20as%20many%20as%20500%20Taiwanese%20technicians%20to%20assist%20with%20construction%20and%20training%20on%20the%20site%2C%20where%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fazgovernor.gov%2Foffice-arizona-governor%2Fnews%2F2023%2F08%2Fgovernor-katie-hobbs-joined-adosh-and-tsmc-arizona-announce%5C%22%3E12%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20work%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Arizona%20Pipe%20Trades%20469%20Union%2C%20a%20labor%20union%20that%20says%20it%20represents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fazpipetrades.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%204%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20pipe%20fitters%2C%20plumbers%2C%20welders%2C%20and%20heating%2C%20ventilation%2C%20and%20air-conditioning%20technicians%2C%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-jobs-taiwan-semiconductor-chip-worker-skills-work-ethic-2023-8%5C%22%3Epetition%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20urge%20US%20lawmakers%20to%20deny%20these%20visas.%20The%20union%20says%20that%20TSMC%20has%20deliberately%20misrepresented%20the%20skillset%20of%20Arizona's%20workforce%20and%20has%20expressed%20concern%20that%20US%20workers%20will%20ultimately%20be%20replaced%20by%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotectazworkers.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeap%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20Taiwanese%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20keep%20saying%20we're%20slowing%20them%20down%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20giving%20us%20the%20information%20we%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20pipe%20cutter%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20the%20Arizona%20site%20for%20roughly%20a%20year%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20us%20are%20capable%20of%20doing%20it%20if%20you%20gave%20us%20the%20correct%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Phoenix%20workers%20spoke%20with%20Insider%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20for%20fear%20of%20professional%20repercussions.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSMC%2C%20however%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20incoming%20Taiwanese%20workers%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-taiwan-semiconductor-phoenix-arizona-factory-chipmaker-job-qualification-debate-2023-8%5C%22%3Enot%20be%20a%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20US%20jobs.%20A%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20that%20at%20this%20stage%20in%20the%20construction%20process%2C%20it's%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20practice%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20local%20workforce%20and%20international%20experienced%20staff%20to%20ensure%20the%20highest-quality%20execution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20did%20not%20respond%20specifically%20to%20the%20accusations%20of%20management%20problems%20on%20the%20site%2C%20but%20a%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BTSMC%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20that%20working%20conditions%20in%20its%20supply%20chains%20are%20safe%2C%20that%20workers%20are%20treated%20with%20respect%20and%20dignity%2C%20and%20that%20business%20operations%20are%20environmentally%20responsible%20and%20conducted%20ethically.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'TSMC%20wants%20you%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%20with%20as%20little%20amount%20of%20information%20and%20as%20fast%20as%20possible'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Arizona%20pipe%20cutter%20said%20the%20construction%20delay%20was%20%26quot%3B100%25%20a%20management%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it's%20not%20that%20US%20workers%20didn't%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20build%20the%20factory%20but%20that%20they're%20just%20not%20being%20given%20sufficient%20resources%20to%20do%20the%20job.%20He%20and%20many%20other%20workers%20on%20the%20site%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20worked%20at%20the%20chipmaker%20Intel%20in%20a%20similar%20capacity%20in%20the%20past%2C%20so%20they%20know%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Intel%2C%20they%20can%20give%20me%20a%20package%20that%20says%2C%20'Hey%2C%20this%20is%20the%20equipment%20that%20I%20want%20you%20to%20build.%20This%20is%20the%20deadline.%20These%20are%20the%20standards.'%20Everything%20you%20could%20think%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20essentially%2C%20TSMC%20is%20the%20exact%20opposite.%20They%20just%20say%2C%20'Build%20this.'%20And%20I%20don't%20get%20the%20blueprints.%20There's%20no%20planning.%20They%20essentially%20assume%20everybody%20just%20knows%20how%20to%20do%20the%20job.%20But%20I%20can't%20read%20your%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20the%20extensive%20blueprints%20he's%20used%20to%2C%20he%20said%20that%20almost%20all%20of%20his%20work%20at%20TSMC%20was%20done%20by%20referring%20to%20emails%20and%20pictures%20that%20sometimes%20included%20difficult-to-decipher%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTSMC%20wants%20you%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%20with%20as%20little%20amount%20of%20information%20and%20as%20fast%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F04%2Ftechnology%2Ftsmc-mark-liu.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20managerial%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20fueled%20in%20part%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-jobs-taiwan-semiconductor-chip-worker-skills-work-ethic-2023-8%5C%22%3Ecultural%20differences%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20TSMC%20and%20US%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20had%20been%20among%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20factory's%20delay.%20In%20February%2C%20TSMC%20employees%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F02%2F22%2Ftechnology%2Ftsmc-arizona-factory-tensions.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Times%20that%20American%20workers%20were%20difficult%20to%20manage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pipe%20cutter%20said%20that%20TSMC%20and%20its%20key%20contractors%20were%20largely%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20management%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20in%20these%20buildings%20after%20they're%20fully%20complete'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20pipe%20cutter%20and%20a%20welder%20at%20the%20Phoenix%20site%20told%20Insider%20they'd%20had%20problems%20getting%20the%20proper%20materials%20needed%20to%20complete%20their%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20issue%20holding%20American%20workers%2C%20or%20any%20workers%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20back%20is%20lack%20of%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20welder%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20sometimes%20had%20to%20wait%20days%20to%20receive%20what%20he%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20they've%20made%20it%20this%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pipe%20cutter%20said%20of%20TSMC%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20the%20Wild%20West.%20Everyone's%20got%20a%20job%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%20just%20let%20you%20all%20run.%20And%20it's%20with%20no%20coordination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20building-code%20violations%20were%20common%20as%20well%2C%20which%20had%20also%20slowed%20down%20construction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20we'll%20have%20to%20do%20work%20two%20or%20three%20times%20because%20they're%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20this%20is%20how%20we%20do%20it%20in%20Taiwan%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20build%20it%20exactly%20how%20they%20want%20it%2C%20but%20then%20as%20soon%20as%20it's%20put%20in%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20it%20because%20it's%20illegal.%20It's%20against%20international%20building%20code.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pipe%20cutter%20said%20that%20safety%20violations%20are%20also%20common%20on%20the%20site.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20said%20in%20one%20instance%2C%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20pounds%20of%20weight%26quot%3B%20were%20loosely%20hanging%2020%20to%2030%20feet%20above%20workers'%20heads%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20big%20safety%20violation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20many%20Taiwanese%20workers%20on%20the%20site%20wore%20tennis%20shoes%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20boots%20%E2%80%94%20and%20didn't%20wear%20safety%20glasses%20or%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20complaining%20about%20one%20safety%20issue%20for%20two%20straight%20weeks%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20spoke%20with%20a%20company%20safety%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20literally%20told%20me%20to%20my%20face%20that%20we're%20only%20here%20for%20insurance%20purposes%20%E2%80%94%20they%20won't%20let%20us%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20company's%20desire%20to%20meet%20baseline%20safety%20requirements.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20when%20I%20gave%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pipe%20cutter%20isn't%20the%20only%20worker%20who%20has%20raised%20safety%20concerns.%20In%20June%2C%20The%20American%20Prospect%20reported%20that%20workers%20said%20injuries%20and%20safety%20violations%20were%20common%20on%20the%20construction%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20easily%20the%20most%20unsafe%20site%20I've%20ever%20walked%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Luke%20Kasper%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20a%20union%20for%20sheet-metal%20workers%2C%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprospect.org%2Flabor%2F2023-06-22-tsmc-semiconductor-factory-phoenix-accidents%2F%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%222a12233e56c671545e03c9981f378fda%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprospect.org%2Flabor%2F2023-06-22-tsmc-semiconductor-factory-phoenix-accidents%2F%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSMC%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffronterasdesk.org%2Fcontent%2F1851968%2Freporter-finds-labor-safety-concerns-tsmc-rushes-build-chip-plants-phoenix%5C%22%3Edefended%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20commitment%20to%20safety.%20When%20asked%20whether%20there%20were%20any%20safety%20issues%20on%20the%20site%2C%20the%20company%20said%20that%20it%20was%20regularly%20audited%20against%20known%20safety%20standards%20and%20that%20it%20conducted%20its%20own%20internal%20audits%20of%20safety%20records%20against%20state%20and%20national%20figures.%20The%20company%20said%20that%20in%20Arizona%2C%20its%20%26quot%3Brecordable%20safety%20incident%20rate%26quot%3B%20was%20nearly%2080%25%20lower%20than%20nationally%20reported%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTSMC%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20workplace%20safety%20in%20the%20operation%20of%20all%20our%20facilities%2C%20along%20with%20each%20of%20our%20active%20construction%20projects%2C%20including%20TSMC%20Arizona%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bizjournals.com%2Fphoenix%2Fnews%2F2023%2F08%2F04%2Ftsmc-workers-arizona-construction.html%5C%22%3Emultiple%3C%2Fa%3E%20health%20and%20safety%20complaints%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20state%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20TSMC%20and%20the%20state%20of%20Arizona%20signed%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmcusercontent.com%2F44a5186aac69c13c570fca36a%2Ffiles%2F80c348e5-8ab6-c4f4-afdf-fe7e61bba418%2FTSMC_Final_Partnership.01.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkplace-safety%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20subject%20the%20company%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yourvalley.net%2Fstories%2Funion-upset-over-health-and-safety-at-tsmc-in-north-phoenix%2C415900%5C%22%3Ehigher%20safety%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20required%20at%20the%20federal%20level%2C%20including%20closer%20oversight%20and%20increased%20training%20and%20safety%20visits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pipe%20cutter%20said%20he's%20worried%20for%20the%20thousands%20of%20workers%20set%20to%20run%20the%20factory%20once%20it's%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20dangerous%20places%20to%20work%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%20in%20a%20semiconductor%20facility%20because%20there%20are%20large%20amounts%20of%20chemicals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BStuff%20is%20going%20to%20break%2C%20and%20when%20it%20does%2C%20these%20are%20nasty%2C%20nasty%20chemicals.%20And%20that's%20my%20worry.%20I%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20in%20these%20buildings%20after%20they're%20fully%20complete.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20not%20like%20we're%20against%20the%20Taiwanese%20workers%20or%20anything.%20TSMC%20is%20the%20problem.'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20entering%20the%20construction%20site%20each%20morning%2C%20both%20workers%20said%20they'd%20experienced%20delays%20at%20every%20step%20of%20the%20process%2C%20from%20hourlong%20security%20lines%20to%20challenges%20procuring%20the%20right%20safety%20gear%2C%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbunny%20suit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20you%20go%20through%20the%20gowning%20process%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20your%20size.%20And%20then%20you%20go%20to%20degown%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20your%20hanger%20or%20somebody%20took%20your%20hanger%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pipe%20cutter%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20literally%20every%20step%20of%20the%20process.%20Everything%20is%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParking%20is%20insane%20out%20there%20with%20the%20vehicles%20and%20traffic%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20welder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20bringing%20over%20more%20Taiwanese%20workers%2C%20the%20welder%20added%2C%20TSMC%20should%20focus%20on%20solving%20these%20other%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20heard%20word%20of%20what%20skills%20we%20are%20lacking%2C%20nor%20any%20word%20or%20info%20at%20all%20on%20what%20or%20when%20we%20will%20be%20trained%20from%20their%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pipe%20cutter%20said%20that%20he%20thought%20the%20workers%20might%20be%20able%20to%20help%20but%20that%20it's%20not%20because%20US%20workers%20lacked%20skills%20or%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20TSMC%20saying%20that%20they%20need%20the%20skilled%20workers%2C%20what%20they%20really%20mean%20is%20they%20want%20the%20cheaper%20workers%2C%20their%20guys%2C%20to%20come%20over%20here%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20tell%20them%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20literally%20just%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20this%20whole%20row%2C%20go%20build%20it.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20we're%20against%20the%20Taiwanese%20workers%20or%20anything.%20We're%20against%20TSMC.%20TSMC%20is%20the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20workers%20said%20that%20they're%20sticking%20it%20out%20because%20the%20job%20paid%20well%20enough%20but%20that%20they%20hoped%20to%20eventually%20find%20other%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20worst%20job%20that%20any%20of%20us%20have%20ever%20had%2C%20as%20far%20as%20safety%20and%20quality%20and%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pipe%20cutter%20said.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20guy%20that%20I%20know%20is%20leaving%20this%20job%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20the%20semiconductor-chip%20industry%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20tell%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%228fb9ce7f5f77b7c71300026184abf261%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-phoenix-arizona-chip-factory-taiwan-semiconductor-management-safety-workers-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692785701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64