Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETragedy%20was%20narrowly%20averted%20at%20Delhi%20airport%20this%20afternoon%20after%20a%20Vistara%20flight%20from%20Ahmedabad%20and%20another%20plane%20of%20the%20same%20airline%20-%20the%20two%20carrying%20around%20300%20people%20in%20total%20-%20thanks%20to%20an%20alert%20pilot%20on%20the%20former%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ahmedabad-Delhi%20flight%20had%20just%20landed%20and%20had%20been%20instructed%20by%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20to%20cross%20an%20active%20runway%20to%20reach%20the%20parking%20bay.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fvistara-airlines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVistara%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20Delhi-Bagdogra%20flight%20had%20been%20given%20permission%20to%20take%20off%20on%20that%20same%20runway%20and%20a%20collision%20was%20only%20avoided%20thanks%20to%2045-year-old%20Captain%20Sonu%20Gill%20on%20the%20Ahmedabad-Delhi%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20planes%20were%201.8%20km%2C%20or%201%2C800%20metres%2C%20apart%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20if%20the%20pilot%20had%20not%20warned%20ATC%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20other%20plane%2C%20the%20outcome%20could%20have%20been%20disastrous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%2C%20Vistara%20flight%20VTI926%20had%20landed%20on%20Runway%2029L%20and%20told%20by%20ATC%20to%20cross%20Runway%2029R%20en%20route%20to%20its%20parking%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ATC%20official%20'momentarily%20forgot'%20instructions%20given%20to%20VTI926%20and%20told%20flight%20VTI725%20to%20take-off%20from%20Runway%2029R.%20The%20regulator's%20statement%20said%20the%20ATC%20'on%20realisation%20of%20the%20error%2C%20based%20on%20input%20from%20VTI926%2C%20tower%20controller%20instructed%20VTI725%20to%20cancel%20take-off'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aviation%20regulator%20said%20an%20'alert%20pilot%20in%20the%20aircraft%20crossing%20the%20runway%20(VTI926)%20alerted%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20and%20the%20aircraft%20on%20its%20take-off%20run%20(VTI725)%20was%20ordered%20to%20abort%20take-off'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%20the%20DGCA%20has%20derostered%20the%20ATC%20official%20responsible%20for%20the%20runway%20incursion%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-Bagdogra%20flight%20retreated%20from%20the%20active%20runway%20immediately%20after%20being%20ordered%20to%20abort%20its%20take-off%20and%20returned%20to%20its%20parking%20bay.%20Officials%20told%20PTI%20the%20plane%20was%20refuelled%20to%20ensure%20it%20had%20enough%20fuel%20for%20the%20second%20take-off%20attempt%20and%20to%20return%20to%20Delhi%20if%20the%20pilot%20encountered%20bad%20weather%20conditions%20at%20or%20en%20route%20to%20Bagdogra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20passengers%20became%20a%20little%20apprehensive%20when%20the%20pilot%20of%20the%20flight%20bound%20for%20Bagdogra%20announced%20that%20the%20plane%20will%20not%20take%20off%20due%20to%20instructions%20from%20ATC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtocol%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20is%20that%20no%20aircraft%20or%20vehicle%20movement%20is%20allowed%20when%20a%20plane%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20take-off%20or%20landing.%20Captain%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20a%20senior%20pilot%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Safety%20Matters%20Foundation%2C%20told%20PTI%20flight%20ops%20'from%20closely%20spaced%20runways%20require%20enhanced%20monitoring%20and%20stricter%20compliance%20with%20SOPs%20to%20avoid%20a%20potential%20traffic%20collision'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-Bagdogra%20flight%20was%20taking%20off%20from%20the%20newly%20inaugurated%20runway%20and%20the%20second%20Vistara%20flight%2C%20after%20landing%20on%20a%20parallel%20runway%2C%20was%20moving%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20same%20runway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692784560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3