elf%3A%20What%20is%20one%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20to%20make%20the%20landlord's%20life%20easier%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStartup%20costs%20for%20renting%20on%20Airbnb%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20need%20to%20have%20money%20to%20start.%20For%20me%2C%20this%20was%20around%20%246%2C000%2C%20but%20it%20will%20very%20much%20depend%20on%20what%20city%20you%20are%20starting%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20one%20of%20those%20businesses%20where%20you%20can%20start%20at%20zero%20dollars.%20Even%20without%20owning%20the%20home%2C%20it%20can%20be%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20my%20first%20place%2C%20I%20paid%20a%20moving%20fee%2C%20I%20purchased%20furniture%2C%20and%20I%20hired%20a%20photographer%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20I%20had%20to%20get%20short%20term%20renters%20insurance%2C%20and%20install%20cameras%20on%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20rental.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20I%20needed%20in%20order%20to%20start%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20rent.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20sometimes%20landlords%20will%20ask%20for%202x%20the%20regular%20rent.%20However%2C%20that%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20make%20a%20profit%2C%20so%20I%20stay%20away%20from%20those.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20vary%20for%20you%2C%20in%20my%20experience%20a%20cost%20breakdown%20might%20look%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMoving%20fee%3A%20usually%20varies%20on%20which%20mover%20I%20am%20using%2C%20sometimes%20it's%20as%20low%20as%20%24200%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPhotographer%3A%20Ranges%20from%20%24100%20to%20%24500%2B%20for%20professional%20property%20photos%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFurniture%3A%20Ranges%20from%20%242%2C500%20-%20%248%2C000%20depending%20on%20the%20property%20size%20and%20style%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3ERent%3A%20Sometimes%20landlords%20ask%20for%202x%20the%20rent%20upfront%2C%20but%20I%20stay%20away%20from%20those%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20handle%20repairs%20and%20damages%20in%20your%20Airbnb%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERepairs%20are%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20things%20to%20consider.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20had%20people%20break%20chairs%2C%20and%20I've%20even%20had%20one%20woman%20break%20a%20bed%20frame.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20damages%20the%20Airbnb%2C%20you%20have%20to%20consider%20what%20you'll%20do%20when%20that%20happens.%20Will%20you%20fix%20it%20yourself%3F%20Will%20you%20hire%20maintenance%3F%20One%20option%20is%20to%20use%20a%20site%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd8210018a6cec1427106cf77361dedd3db4eb7c2142375ecf6b885b988a2da65%26postID%3D64dbb76ae64f191fc5ea70c1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.taskrabbit.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaskrabbit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20freelance%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girlboss%20Getaway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64de48fe4ef9f30019f926fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20in%20the%20Girlboss%20Getaway%2C%20one%20of%20my%20Airbnb%20units.%3Cp%3EMonica%20White%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20stand%20out%20on%20Airbnb%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20all%20of%20these%20things%20into%20consideration%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20get%20started.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20consider%20who%20you%20want%20to%20rent%20to.%20Zeroing%20in%20on%20your%20potential%20customer%20will%20help%20with%20your%20listing%3A%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20rent%20to%20vacationers%2C%20or%20those%20who%20travel%20for%20work%2C%20or%20student%20relocators%3F%20It%20helps%20to%20focus%20on%20one%20lane%20instead%20of%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20think%20about%20SEO%20(search%20engine%20optimization).%20Sometimes%20people%20have%20really%20good%20units%2C%20but%20because%20they%20are%20on%20the%20fourth%20page%20of%20Airbnb%20their%20homes%20aren't%20easily%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20combat%20this%2C%20I've%20used%20photographers%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20photos%20were%20really%20good%2C%20and%20then%20I'd%20detail%20all%20of%20the%20special%20amenities%20in%20my%20unit%20to%20boost%20my%20posts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20helps%20to%20add%20nice%20touches%20to%20short-term%20rentals%2C%20like%20champagne%2C%20wine%2C%20water%20or%20just%20a%20nice%20little%20thank%20you%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20rely%20on%20just%20the%20platform.%20Promote%20your%20listings%20yourself%20and%20do%20what%20you%20can%20to%20stand%20out%20and%20be%20noticeable.%20One%20idea%20is%20to%20share%20your%20listings%20in%20relevant%20Facebook%20groups.%20You%20have%20to%20do%20what%20you%20can%20to%20drive%20traffic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20people%20won't%20be%20interested%20if%20they%20don't%20see%20your%20listing%20enough.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20why%20people%20have%20picked%20mine%20because%20I%20have%20been%20known%20for%20putting%20it%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20renting%20out%20other%20peoples'%20homes%20is%20not%20easy%2C%20but%20with%20the%20right%20mindset%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20tell%20my%20clients%20to%20do%20their%20own%20research%20before%20starting.%20You%20will%20hear%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20say%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20or%20everyone%20is%20doing%20it%2C%20but%20to%20me%20that%20is%20silly.%20Airbnb%20is%20still%20a%20growing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20an%20Airbnb%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20email%20Alyshia%20Hull%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aahull%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eahull%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-made-s