and%20it%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20stuff%20one%20has%20to%20be%20careful%20about.%20Sharing%20details%2C%20Kriti%20revealed%20that%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20is%20not%20all%20%E2%80%9Cflowery.%E2%80%9D%20The%20actress%20recalled%20how%20she%20spotted%20a%20hidden%20camera%20in%20her%20hotel%20room%2C%20during%20the%20shooting%20of%20one%20of%20her%20Kannada%20films.%20Kriti%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhauterrfly.com%2Foriginals%2Fthe-male-feminist-ft-kriti-kharbanda-with-siddharth-aalambayan-episode-45%2F%5C%22%3ESiddharth%20Aalambayan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20this%20one%20incident%20where%20I%20remember%20I%20was%20shooting%20for%20one%20of%20my%20Kannada%20films.%20This%20boy%2C%20who%20used%20to%20work%20at%20the%20hotel%2C%20actually%20left%20a%20camera%20in%20my%20room.%20Me%20and%20my%20staff%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20making%20sure%20that%20there%20is%20actually%20nothing%20popping%20out%20of%20anywhere.%20He%20was%20actually%20not%20a%20pro%20at%20it%2C%20because%20it%20was%20kept%20so%20badly.%20%3Cem%3EVoh%20seedha%20nazar%20mai%20aa%20raha%20tha.%20Set-top%20box%20ke%20piche%20rakha%20tha%20usne.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%5BIt%20was%20pretty%20visible%2C%20as%20it%20was%20kept%20right%20behind%20the%20set-top%20box.%20It's%20scary%20that%20the%20kind%20of%20stuff%20you%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20about.%20It's%20not%20all%20flowery%20in%20our%20industry.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20Kriti%20Kharbanda%20also%20spoke%20about%20non-consensual%20touch.%20The%20actress%20shared%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cso%20upsetting%E2%80%9D%20when%20someone%20tries%20to%20touch%20you%20without%20your%20consent.%20She%20shared%20one%20of%20her%20experiences%20when%20a%20fan%20pinched%20her%20while%20getting%20a%20photograph.%20Kriti%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20came%20and%20stood%20behind%20me%2C%C2%A0like%20next%20to%20me%2C%20and%20he%20tried%20to%20put%20his%20arm%20around%20me.%20So%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBhaiya%20kya%20kar%20rahe%20ho%3F%20Hath%20aage%20karo.%20Toh%20usne%20mujhe%20bahut%20zor%20se%20chuti%20kati%3C%2Fem%3E%20(What%20are%20you%20doing%3F%20Please%20keep%20your%20hands%20away%20and%20then%C2%A0he%20pinched%20me%20very%20badly).%20I%20even%20got%20a%20blood%20clot%2C%20and%20he%20ran.%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20react.%20I%20was%20very%20shocked%20and%20taken%20aback.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpulkit-samrat-loves-to-share-this-cocktail-with-kriti-kharbanda-its-made-of-2592250%5C%22%3EKriti%20Kharbanda%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20worked%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Tamil%2C%20Telugu%20and%20Kannada%20films.%20She%20is%20best%20known%20for%20her%20work%20in%20%3Cem%3EHousefull%204%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EPagalpanti.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Kriti%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20%3Cem%3E14%20Phere%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20alongside%20Vikrant%20Massey.%20Apart%20from%20her%20films%20and%20fashion%20choices%2C%20Kriti%20Kharbanda%20often%20makes%20headlines%20for%20her%20relationship%20with%20actor%20Pulkit%20Samrat.%20The%20lovebirds%20were%20co-stars%20in%20the%202018%20film%20%3Cem%3EVeerey%20Ki%20Wedding%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20their%20first%20film%20together.%20Kriti%20and%20Pulkit%20went%20on%20to%20work%20in%20the%202019-release%20comedy%20film%20%3Cem%3EPagalpanti%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20Bejoy%20Nambiar's%20%3Cem%3ETaish%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKriti%20Kharbanda%20and%20Pulkit%20Samrat%20made%20their%20relationship%20official%20in%202019.%20Pulkit%20was%20previously%20married%20to%20Salman%20Khan's%20rakhi%20sister%20Shweta%20Rohira.%20The%20duo%20parted%20ways%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692783420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Furtb6gpo_kriti-_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkriti-kharbanda-reveals-a