ut%20staff%20on%20flights%20between%20Germany%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20stay%20awake%20overnight%20and%20be%20attentive%20to%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20Lufthansa%20Airlines%20worked%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%20on%20a%20round-trip%20between%20Germany%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20serving%20passengers%20onboard%20the%20German%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Jens%20Ritter%20detailed%20his%20experiences%20in%20a%20recent%20LinkedIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd0659bc10d9bea225fffcdee21ebd3a9d25fbae972355060e7aaf0c59c8c3765%26postID%3D64e49d9344625f836ff841f7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Ffeed%252Fupdate%252Furn%253Ali%253Aactivity%253A7098227992987852800%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20you%20need%20to%20change%20perspectives%20in%20order%20to%20gain%20new%20insights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Lufthansa%20spokesperson%2C%20Ritter%20worked%20on%20an%20outbound%20and%20return%20flight%20between%20Frankfurt%20in%20Germany%20and%20Bahrain.%20The%20flight%20stopped%20at%20Riyadh%20in%20Saudia%20Arabia%20both%20ways%2C%20making%20it%20a%20four-leg%20journey.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERitter's%20tasks%20involved%20looking%20after%20business%20class%20passengers%20on%20the%20departing%20flight%2C%20and%20then%20in%20economy%20class%20overnight%20on%20the%20way%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20interesting%20to%20address%20the%20guests'%20wishes%20individually%2C%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20different%20energy%20everyone%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20CEO%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwas%20amazed%20by%20how%20much%20there%20is%20to%20organize%2C%20especially%20if%20something%20doesn't%20go%20as%20planned.%26quot%3B%20Ritter%20explained%20that%20the%20meals%20loa