20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETamara%20Smith%20has%20always%20worked%20side%20hustles%20by%20making%20deliveries%20or%20by%20driving%20for%20ride-share%20apps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Dallas-based%20aircraft%20dispatcher%20said%20Alto%20is%20more%20professional%20than%20her%20other%20side%20hustles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20luxury%20ride-sharing%20app%20offers%20drivers%20health%20benefits%20and%20cars%20to%20drive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Tamara%20Smith%2C%20a%20Dallas-based%20driver%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fridealto.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAlto%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20high-end%20ride-share%20app%20operating%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Houston%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Miami%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20side%20hustle%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20in%20this%20society%2C%20you%20have%20to.%20I%20work%20as%20an%20aircraft%20dispatcher%20as%20my%20day%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20family%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wife%2C%20a%20daughter%20in%20college%2C%20and%20a%20teenage%20son%2C%20so%20extra%20money%20is%20always%20good.%20I%20tried%20driving%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20from%202015%20until%202020%20off%20and%20on.%20It%20looked%20simple%20and%20easy%2C%20and%20I%20could%20work%20when%20I%20wanted%20to.%20I%20liked%20side%20hustles%20that%20work%20around%20my%20daily%20life%20and%20my%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20discovered%20Alto%2C%20I%20was%20working%20one%20of%20my%20delivery-driver%20side%20hustles.%20I%20kept%20seeing%20their%20cars%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20at%20Whole%20Foods%2C%20and%20I%20downloaded%20the%20app%20to%20see%20what%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlto%20is%20a%20luxury%2C%20membership-based%20car-service%20app%20that%20operates%20a%20fleet%20of%20cars%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Houston%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Miami%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20it%20on%20my%20phone%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20because%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20using%20it%20to%20take%20rides%2C%20but%20when%20I%20started%20doing%20my%20research%20on%20the%20company%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20immediately%20a%20different%20vibe%20compared%20to%20other%20side%20hustles%20I'd%20done%20before.%20I%20had%20to%20send%20in%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20I%20had%20a%20real%20interview%2C%20so%20it%20was%20just%20like%20getting%20a%20more%20traditional%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlto%20drivers%20work%20flexible%20shifts%20and%20get%20paid%20by%20the%20hour%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%20for%20me%20between%20Alto%20and%20other%20side%20hustles%20I've%20worked%20is%20that%20it%20offers%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20work%20one%2010-hour%20shift%20a%20week%2C%20I%20can%20remain%20an%20Alto%20driver%2C%20and%20as%20a%20driver%20you're%20paid%20by%20the%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20not%20by%20how%20many%20trips%20you%20book.%20I%20know%20how%20much%20money%20I'm%20going%20to%20make%20if%20I%20work%20five%2C%20six%2C%20eight%2C%20or%2010%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20shifts%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Friday%20evenings%20%E2%80%94%20do%20pay%20more.%20I%20feel%20like%20with%20other%20ride-share%20apps%2C%20you're%20hustling%20and%20bustling%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20rides%20and%20rushing%20people%20out%20of%20your%20car%20because%20you%20need%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20rider%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20drove%20for%20Uber%2C%20I%20made%20the%20same%20or%20slightly%20more%20money%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20work%20longer%20hours%20and%20more%20days.%20It%20was%20different%20each%20day%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20stack%20or%20stagger%20shifts%20to%20work%20around%20your%20lifestyle.%20I%20recently%20had%20a%20schedule%20change%20at%20my%20full-time%20job%20to%20mornings%2C%20so%20now%20I%20work%20evenings%20as%20an%20Alto%20driver.%20It's%20been%20easy%20to%20balance%20with%20my%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20have%20one%20day%20where%20I%20have%20a%20window%20of%20at%20least%2010%20hours%20for%20my%20availability%2C%20the%20Alto%20team%20will%20be%20flexible%20about%20making%20sure%20my%20shifts%20don't%20conflict%20with%20my%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDriving%20with%20Alto%20has%20the%20structure%20and%20certainty%20of%20a%20full-time%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Alto%2C%20we%20have%20set%20shifts%2C%20like%20regular%20employees%20going%20into%20an%20office.%20I%20start%20my%20shift%20at%20our%20operations%20office%20located%20across%20the%20street%20from%20one%20of%20our%20major%20airports%20in%20Dallas%2C%20which%20is%20convenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20clock%20in%2C%20and%20the%20lead%20gives%20me%20my%20pouch%20with%20a%20cell%20phone%2C%20a%20credit%20card%20for%20gas%2C%20and%20a%20key%20to%20the%20car.%20I%20check%20my%20car%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20up%20to%20Alto%20standards%2C%20and%20then%20I%20roll%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20Alto%20driver%2C%20you%20also%20have%20the%20option%20to%20get%20health%20benefits%20and%20a%20401(k)%20because%20all%20drivers%20are%20W2%20employees.%20I%20don't%20need%20them%20because%20I%20do%20well%20with%20my%20full-time%20job%20as%20an%20FAA%20dispatcher%20and%20trainer%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20great%20option%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUber%20and%20Lyft%20weren't%20as%20dependable%20as%20a%20driver%20and%20as%20a%20rider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlto%20riders%20make%20me%20feel%20more%20comfortable%20because%20most%20of%20our%20riders%20pay%20a%20monthly%20membership%20fee%2C%20whereas%20with%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%2C%20anyone%20can%20request%20a%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20people%20being%20members%20and%20Alto%20rates%20being%20more%20comparable%20to%20the%20comfort%20and%20luxury%20tiers%20of%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20means%20riders%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20give%20the%20drivers%20and%20cars%20more%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20being%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20I've%20worked%20every%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20mornings%2C%20afternoons%2C%20and%20overnights%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20don't%20feel%20unsafe%2C%20even%20working%20overnight%20by%20myself%20in%20the%20car%20with%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20did%20not%20have%20bad%20passengers%20with%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%2C%20but%20you%20are%20always%20hearing%20about%20attacks%20in%20the%20news%20and%20drunk%20people%20being%20rude%20and%20not%20wanting%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20I%20have%20never%20experienced%20anything%20out%20of%20the%20ordinary%20while%20driving%20for%20Alto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%2C%20you%20never%20know%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20get.%20The%20car%20pulling%20up%20could%20be%20dirty%20or%20the%20wheels%20could%20be%20coming%20off.%20I%20got%20in%20an%20Uber%20in%20New%20Orleans%20once%20and%20the%20driver%20didn't%20have%20a%20back%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20with%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20keep%20my%20car%20clean%20and%20I%20tried%20to%20stay%20groomed%2C%20but%20with%20Alto%2C%20that's%20the%20standard.%20You%20come%20to%20work%20in%20your%20uniform%20with%20your%20shirt%20tucked%20in%20and%20your%20hat%20on%2C%20so%20it's%20all%20consistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETipping%20isn't%20allowed%20via%20the%20app%2C%20but%20sometimes%20we%20get%20cash%20tips.%20Cash%20tips%20are%20amazing%20compared%20to%20other%20ride-share%20apps.%20It's%20always%20great%20tips%20every%20time%20you%20get%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20drawback%20with%20Alto%20would%20be%20that%20it's%20still%20new%2C%20and%20rules%20change%20often%2C%20which%20I%20can%20understand%2C%20but%20I%20know%20with%20newer%20people%2C%20it%20can%20take%20a%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20response%20to%20Tamara%20Smith's%20concerns%20about%20Uber%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20ridesharing%20app%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20take%20the%20safety%20of%20riders%20and%20drivers%20seriously%2C%20and%20have%20designed%20in-app%20safety%20features%20that%20leverage%20technology%2C%20like%20GPS%20tracking%20on%20every%20trip%2C%20RideCheck%2C%20and%20the%20in-app%20Emergency%20Button%2C%20to%20help%20raise%20the%20bar.%20Our%20commitment%20is%20unwavering%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20build%20policies%20and%20features%20that%20enhance%20safety%20on%20the%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELyft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falto-rideshare-driver-best-driving-side-hustle-uber-lyft-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692782765000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df7e43bd98a60019790c75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falto-rideshare-driver-best-driving-side-hustle-uber-lyft-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Alto%20rideshare%20driver%20says%20it's%20a%20better%20side%20hustle%20than%20driving%20for%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%20because%20she's%20paid%20hourly%20and%20can%20get%20health%20insurance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jamie%20Killin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falto-rideshare-driver-best-driving-side-hustle-uber-lyft-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rakhi%20Sawant%20'shocked'%20after%20best%20friend%20files%20police%20complaint%20against%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692782657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102979427%2Cimgsize-51652.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2F