were%20given%20permission%20at%20the%20same%20time%20but%20ATC%20took%20control%20immediately.%20The%20ATC%20(Air%20Traffic%20Control)%20officer%20on%20duty%20asked%20Vistara%20flight%20to%20abort%20take-off%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%2C%20who%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20developments%2C%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-Bagdogra%20flight%20returned%20to%20the%20parking%20bay%20from%20the%20active%20runway%20immediately%20after%20take-off%20was%20aborted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20it%20was%20refuelled%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20plane%20had%20enough%20fuel%20to%20return%20to%20Delhi%20if%20the%20pilot%20encountered%20bad%20weather%20conditions%20at%20Bagdogra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20braking%20system%20was%20also%20checked%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20airport%20officials%2C%20if%20the%20flight%20taking%20off%20was%20not%20stopped%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20a%20major%20accident%20could%20have%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20(SOP)%2C%20no%20aircraft%20or%20vehicle%20movement%20is%20allowed%20during%20the%20process%20of%20take-off%20and%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20passengers%20became%20a%20little%20apprehensive%20when%20the%20pilot%20of%20the%20flight%20bound%20for%20Bagdogra%20announced%20that%20the%20plane%20will%20not%20take%20off%20due%20to%20instructions%20from%20ATC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20pilot%20and%20founder%20of%20Safety%20Matters%20Foundation%2C%20Capt%20Amit%20Singh%20said%20that%20flight%20operations%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20closely%20spaced%20runways%20require%20enhanced%20monitoring%20and%20stricter%20compliance%20with%20SOPs%20to%20avoid%20a%20potential%20traffic%20collision%20due%20to%20the%20proximity%20of%20the%20flight%20path%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNormally%20a%20take-off%20clearance%20is%20not%20issued%20to%20an%20aircraft%20on%20one%20runway%20unless%20the%20aircraft%20on%20the%20second%20runway%20has%20landed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20due%20to%20a%20lapse%20if%20the%20aircraft%20is%20permitted%20to%20take%20off%20from%20one%20runway%20and%20the%20aircraft%20approaching%20on%20the%20second%20runway%20decides%20to%20abort%20the%20landing%20and%20carry%20out%20a%20go-around%20to%20climb%20ahead%2C%20the%20flight%20path%20of%20the%20two%20aircraft%20in%20the%20air%20may%20come%20in%20conflict%20since%20the%20runway%20they%20were%20aligned%20to%20were%20closely%20spaced%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EANI%20contacted%20Vistara%20but%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692781020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F08lqqp18_vistara-generic_625x300_30_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-airport-2-vistara-planes-cleared-for-take-off-landing-at-same-time-in-delhi-mishap-averted-4321574%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20major%20mishap%20was%20averted%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20as%20a%20Vistara%20Airlines%20aircraft%20was%20given%20permission%20for%20take-off%20while%20another%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20landing.%20The%20take-off%20was%20aborted%20after%20instructions%20from%20ATC.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-airport-2-vistara-planes-cleared-for-take-off-landing-at-same-time-in-delhi-mishap-averted-4321574%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-airport-2-vistara-planes-cleared-for-take-off-landing-at-same-time-in-delhi-mishap-averted-4321574%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co