20tracking%20the%20lander's%20gradual%20descent.%20A%2032-metre%20dish%20antenna%2C%20India's%20largest%2C%20at%20Byalalu%20near%20Bengaluru%20is%20tracking%20Chandrayaan-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20times%20when%20the%20lander%20moves%20to%20a%20shadow%20region%20and%20cannot%20be%20tracked%20from%20here.%20This%20is%20where%20deep%20space%20networks%20of%20NASA%20and%20ESA%20come%20in.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20a%20free%20service.%20India%20is%20paying%20for%20this%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20many%20antennas%20it%20uses%20and%20for%20what%20duration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20the%20lander%20is%20not%20in%20the%20view%20of%20our%20antenna%2C%20the%20NASA%20or%20ESA%20communicates%20with%20the%20lander%20and%20relay%20the%20information%20to%20the%20mission%20operations%20team%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%2C%20however%2C%20be%20made%20clear%20that%20these%20networks%20assisting%20ISRO%20have%20no%20say%20in%20what%20is%20to%20be%20done%20or%20communicated%20to%20the%20lander.%20That%20control%20rests%20with%20the%20mission%20operations%20team%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20they%20function%20only%20as%20a%20communication%20link%20when%20ISRO%20can't%20access%20the%20lander%20through%20its%20own%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20expected%20to%20land%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20moon%20around%206%20pm.%20Events%20of%20mass%20viewing%20have%20been%20organised%20across%20the%20country%20and%20people%20are%20holding%20prayers%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20mission.%20The%20suspense%20is%20particularly%20high%20after%20Russia's%20moon%20mission%20ended%20in%20a%20crash%20of%20its%20Luna-25%20spacecraft%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692776880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fgicjkphg_isro_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-chandrayaan-updates-isro-nasa-european-space-agency-how-nasa-european-