l%20checks%20and%20await%20the%20sunrise%20at%20the%20designated%20landing%20site%2C%20ISRO%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20powered%20descent%20--%20to%20achieve%20soft-landing%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20--%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20initiated%20at%20around%205%3A45%20pm%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20the%20scheduled%20touch-down%2C%20ISRO%20on%20Tuesday%20confirmed%20that%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20is%20on%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20second%20attempt%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon%20after%20a%20failure%20in%202019%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20display%20of%20the%20tenacity%20of%20its%20scientific%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20attempt%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20flown%20to%20Bengaluru%20to%20watch%20the%20planned%20touch%20down%20of%20the%20lander.%20Even%20the%20mission%20failed%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20witnessed%20a%20heartfelt%20moment%20between%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20K%20Sivan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20hugged%20and%20consoled%20Mr%20Sivan%20as%20he%20broke%20down%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20space%20agency%20announced%20it%20lost%20contact%20with%20the%20lander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692774060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fjmp57jhg_modi_650x400_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-witness-chandrayaan-3-moon-landing-attempt-virtually-from-south-africa-4321415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20is%20in%20South%20Africa%20to%20attend%20the%20BRICS%20Summit%2C%20will%20today%20virtually%20witness%20the%20landing%20attempt%20of%20India's%20moon%20mission%20-%20Chandrayaan-3.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-witness-chandrayaan-3-moon-landing-attempt-virtually-from-south-africa-4321415%22%2C%22cdnAmp