20seeds).%20This%20gave%20him%20yet%20another%20harvest%20of%204%2C000%20kg%20of%20brown%20top%20millets%2C%20which%20he%20then%20sold%20for%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20almost%20double%20my%20previous%20revenue%20without%20sowing%20new%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomashekar%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20glad%20he%20can%20help%20his%20community.%20His%20beliefs%20in%20good%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20a%20love%20for%20farming%20have%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%20and%20helped%20him%20scale%20his%20empire%20to%20what%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692021061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-1692018453.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Somashekar%20Pogula's%20father%20passed%20away%20in%202013%2C%20it%20left%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20him.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20enable%20people%20to%20eat%20right%20and%20help%20farmers%20earn%20better%2C%20he%20started%20Adithi%20Millets%20in%20Kurnool%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327220%2Fandhra-pradesh-somashekar-pogula-started-adithi-millets-empower-organic-farmers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20Had%20No%20Idea%20How%20Gay%20People%20Exist%E2%80%99%3A%20Queer%20Comedian%20Breaks%20Barriers%20in%20Comedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENavin%20Noronha%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F153761%2Fdeepika-mhatre-mumbai-domestic-help-stand-up-comedian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estand-up%20comic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20podcaster%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20was%2014%20when%20he%20knew%20he%20was%20queer%20(gay).%20But%20he%20was%20also%20raised%20as%20a%20staunch%20Catholic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20to%20first%20do%20away%20with%20that%20%5Bfeeling%20attracted%20to%20boys%5D%20by%20joining%20Bible%20camps.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20Class%208%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20priests%20coming%20to%20our%20church%20recognised%20me%20as%20a%20very%20talented%20and%20outspoken%20child.%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20I%20was%20groomed%20to%20become%20a%20Catholic%20priest.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20I%20like%20men%20and%20that%20duality%20set%20in.%20So%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20about%20it%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20until%20I%20was%2019%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Navin%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavin%20first%20came%20out%20to%20his%20best%20friend%20Amit%2C%20who%20he%20knew%20since%20they%20were%2010.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20knew%20each%20other%20very%20well%2C%20although%20we%20were%20never%20friends%20who%20spoke%20about%20personal%20stuff.%20So%2C%20when%20I%20came%20out%20to%20him%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20fact.%20I%20just%20kind%20of%20came%20out%20to%20him%20and%20nothing%20changed%20after%20that%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20being%20gay%20is%20really.%20People%20who%20know%20you%2C%20know%20you%20for%20who%20you%20are.%20What%20gender%20you%20sleep%20with%20barely%20makes%20a%20difference%20to%20them%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20was%2021%20and%20in%20his%20third%20year%20of%20college%2C%20he%20had%20come%20out%20to%20most%20of%20his%20friends.%20He%20says%20he%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20tell%20all%20his%20friends%20and%20acquaintances%20that%20he%20was%20gay%20because%20he%20had%20begun%20feeling%20left%20out%20from%20their%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20wanted%20to%20chime%20in%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20people%20would%20share%20weird%20notions%20of%20what%20gay%20people%20are%20with%20me.%20Listening%20to%20them%2C%20I%20found%20some%20of%20their%20notions%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F152754%2Fiit-madras-kaushik-section-377-supreme-court%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egay%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20hilarious.%20They%20had%20no%20idea%20about%20gay%20people%20and%20how%20we%20exist.%20That%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20my%20first%20comedy%20set%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20Comedian%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028.jpg%201365w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327138%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENavin%20Noronha%20is%20giving%20a%20platform%20to%20other%20queer%20comedians.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQueer%20comics%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Navin%20was%2023%2C%20he%20started%20doing%20stand-up%20comedy%20seriously.%20During%20these%20open%20mics%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20take%20all%20these%20notions%20that%20his%20friends%20had%20of%20gay%20people%2C%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20jokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20he%20came%20out%20to%20his%20friend%2012%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20and%20began%20performing%20as%20a%20full-time%20comic%20eight%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20has%20changed.%20After%20years%20of%20touring%2C%20he%20released%20his%20first%20special%20%E2%80%98The%20Good%20Child%E2%80%99%20on%20YouTube%20in%20late%20June%202023.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Navin%20has%20not%20only%20spread%20laughter%2C%20but%20also%20curated%20a%20lineup%20of%20LGBTQ%2B%20performers.%20They%20went%20on%20tour%20to%20Delhi%20in%20June%20and%20Mumbai%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20were%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20us%20comics%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Ayushi%20Jagad%2C%20Manvendra%20Singh%2C%20Ankur%20Tangde%20and%20I%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20openly%20talking%20about%20our%20queer%20lives.%20Today%2C%20we%20have%20about%2020%20comics%20who%20are%20out%20and%20proud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20done%20sold%20out%20shows%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Navin.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20it%20takes%20grit%2C%20money%2C%20and%20resources%20to%20set%20up%20these%20shows.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20queer%20comics%2C%20we%20want%20to%20create%20spaces%20where%20other%20queer%20people%20can%20just%20vibe%2C%20thrive%20and%20nobody%20can%20tell%20us%20anything.%20I%20live%20for%20that.%20What%20we%20have%20done%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20is%20try%20our%20best%20to%20make%20this%20a%20safer%20space%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%20Today%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20venues%20are%20pro-queer%20rights%20like%20Depot%2048%20in%20Delhi.%20Another%20example%20is%20the%20Social%20chain%20of%20cafes%2C%20which%20has%20been%20so%20proactive.%20They%20host%20the%20Queer%20Comedy%20Mic%20for%20us%20too.%20These%20are%20small%20steps%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20what%20we%20can%20joyfully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Navin%20utilises%20his%20public%20speaking%20engagements%20to%20address%20corporate%20and%20educational%20spaces%2C%20fostering%20understanding%20and%20inclusivity%20for%20queer%20individuals%20in%20professional%20and%20academic%20environments.%20His%20impact%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%20Indian%20comedy%20circuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20Comedian%20from%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-300x159.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-500x264.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-768x406.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327140%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20more%20I%20delved%20into%20my%20queer%20self%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20my%20reality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20out%2C%20Navin%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20fearful%20of%20talking%20about%20his%20sexuality%2C%20and%20credits%20some%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98seniors%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20business%20for%20giving%20out%20useful%20pointers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20senior%20comics%20%E2%80%94%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20Sapan%20Verma%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20would%20advise%20us%20that%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20perfect%20that%20one%20five-minute%20set%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20open%20mic%20circuit%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20of%20us%20performing%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20you%20also%20have%20to%20stand%20out.%20I%20knew%20that%20being%20queer%20on%20a%20given%20lineup%20was%20definitely%20going%20to%20be%20a%20standout%20because%20nobody%20%5Bin%20the%20audience%5D%20knew%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20five-minute%20set%20Navin%20tried%20to%20perfect%20was%20about%20his%20coming%20out%20experiences.%20However%2C%20his%20set%20was%20initially%20not%20doing%20well.%20Paying%20Rs%20300%20to%20just%20travel%20from%20North%20Bombay%20to%20South%20Bombay%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%20300%20to%20perform%20an%20open%20mic%20set%20at%20the%20Canvas%20Laugh%20Club%20initially%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20a%20worthwhile%20pursuit.%20Naturally%2C%20some%20doubts%20had%20begun%20to%20creep%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAllaying%20my%20doubts%2C%20comics%20like%20Sapan%20and%20Kaneez%20(Surka)%20were%20kind%20enough%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20break%20it%20%5Bbeing%20gay%5D%20down%20for%20straight%20people%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20concept%20of%20top%20and%20bottom%20means%E2%80%99%3B%20or%20%E2%80%98They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20Grindr%20is.%20They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20have%20no%20idea%20about%20queer%20people%20in%20this%20country%20and%20how%20they%20live%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20pointers%20made%20sense.%20My%20first%20idea%20was%20that%20the%205-minute%20set%20has%20to%20become%20a%2010-minute%20one%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20break%20everything%20down%20slowly%2C%20and%20therein%20the%20humour%20came%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20Navin%20explaining%20top%20and%20bottom%20%5Bsex%20positions%5D%20to%20people.%20These%20jokes%20are%20the%20outcome%20of%20trialling%20them%20for%20years%20before%20implementing%20them%20in%20real%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20when%20I%20say%20jokes%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Kerala%20is%20bottom%2C%20Delhi%20is%20top%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20back%20to%20the%20audience%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20inbuilt%20joke%20as%20well.%20The%20demographic%20of%20the%20country%20also%20is%20very%20vivid%20in%20terms%20of%20sexual%20preferences.%20The%20%E2%80%98top%20and%20bottom%E2%80%99%20joke%20has%20become%20a%20reel%20on%20my%20Instagram%20handle.%20If%20you%20read%20the%20comments%20section%20right%20now%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20gay%20people%20trying%20to%20hook%20up%20with%20each%20other.%20What%20I%20like%20about%20queer%20culture%20is%20that%20we%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Navin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20straights%20to%20gay%20school.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20full%20special%20is%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMl5xm3p3OW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMl5xm3p3OW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2