l%20kids%20are%20the%20same.%20Some%20are%20intellectually%20disabled%20and%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20identify%20their%20homes%20as%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20communicate%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Saurabh%20Maurya%2C%20who%20accompanies%20children%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20case%20of%20Shoaib%2C%20we%20had%20to%20use%20his%20biometrics%20to%20get%20his%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20and%20address%20details%2C%20because%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20communicate%20about%20his%20home%20and%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%20to%20increase%20and%20better%20facilities%20at%20shelter%20homes.%20Also%2C%20coordination%20of%20the%20counterpart%20districts%20also%20matters.%20If%20the%20police%20stations%20there%20are%20not%20active%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20track%20their%20locations.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20one-time%20process.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20continuous%20in%20spearheading%20the%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Himanshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20feels%20that%20this%20work%20is%20also%20part%20of%20his%20duty.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20reunite%20these%20children%20with%20their%20families%2C%20then%20I%20do%20not%20think%20we%20are%20doing%20a%20good%20job.%20What%20we%20do%20is%20just%20part%20of%20my%20legal%20responsibilities.%20There%20have%20been%20moments%20when%20we%20see%20families%20crying%20with%20happiness%20when%20their%20kids%20reach%20home.%20Looking%20at%20their%20smiles%20makes%20your%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu.%20All%20photos%3A%20Saurabh%20Maurya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691761928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-4-1691757772.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IAS%20officer%20Himanshu%20Nagpal%20spearheads%20Mission%20Muskaan%20to%20reunite%20lost%20children%20living%20in%20Varanasi%E2%80%99s%20ghats%2C%20railway%20stations%2C%20and%20temples%20with%20their%20families%20across%20India.%20He%20shares%20how%20he%20does%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Journalist%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Typical%20Himachali%20Homestay%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Sustainable%20Dream%20Where%20Guests%20Can%20Stargaze%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20journalist%20whose%20forte%20lay%20in%20writing%20about%20travel%2C%20culture%20and%20art%20for%2015%20long%20years%2C%20Sanjay%20Austa%20never%20fathomed%20that%20one%20day%2C%20the%20tables%20would%20turn%20%E2%80%94%20he%20and%20his%20journey%20would%20be%20written%20about%20instead.%20As%20he%20settles%20down%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20for%20a%20tete-a-tete%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20every%20decision%20that%20the%20Himachal%20native%20has%20made%20is%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300372%2F8-pocket-friendly-cosy-homestays-in-the-mountains-for-that-scenic-winter-break%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20love%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20culmination%20of%20this%20love%20is%20his%20venture%20%E2%80%98Meen%20Bagh%20Homes%E2%80%99%20that%20he%20started%20in%202017%20as%20a%20step%20towards%20making%20eco%20travel%20possible.%20The%20sustainable%20property%20offers%20city%20folk%20a%20chance%20to%20live%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctypical%20Himachali%20home%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20surrounded%20by%20f