cture%2C%20the%20homestay%20is%20resilient%20to%20the%20extreme%20climates%20seen%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sanjay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20that%20gave%20impetus%20to%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20burning%20desire%20to%20return%20to%20the%20hills%20was%20the%20craving%20to%20be%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%3Eproximity%20to%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20in%202017%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Himachal%20and%20interestingly%2C%20was%20met%20with%20a%20surprising%20turn%20of%20events%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20a%20backstory%20that%20has%20its%20roots%2070%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20had%20built%20a%20building%20in%20the%20same%20area%20where%20the%20now%20famous%20apple%20belt%20of%20Himachal%20is%20located.%20While%20the%20orchards%20continued%20to%20bloom%2C%20the%20building%20had%20been%20in%20a%20dilapidated%20state%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now.%20My%20father%20wanted%20to%20bring%20it%20down%20and%20in%20its%20stead%20build%20a%20more%20modern%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20this%20juncture%20of%20deciding%20what%20to%20do%20with%20the%20property%20that%20Sanjay%20reached%20the%20scene%20and%20proposed%20an%20interesting%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20structure%20built%20by%20my%20grandfather%20was%20in%20the%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Ekumaoni%3C%2Fem%3E%20style%20and%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20draw%20for%20tourists.%20My%20parents%20were%20unsure%20of%20this%20potential%20that%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20house%20as%20Ratnari%20is%20not%20a%20touristy%20place%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20more%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5