ited%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%2C%20Sanjay%20recounts%20feeling%20chilly%20and%20shivering.%20Despite%20the%20dipping%20temperatures%20outside%2C%20the%20homes%20were%20surprisingly%20warm%20and%20cosy%2C%20without%20any%20heaters!%20Perplexed%2C%20Sanjay%20asked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20locals%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20they%20managed%20this%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInsulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20told%20me%2C%20says%20Sanjay.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20allowed%20heat%20to%20stay%20within%20the%20home%20and%20keep%20it%20warm.%E2%80%9D%20He%20was%20quick%20to%20draw%20comparisons%20between%20this%20model%20and%20the%20ones%20that%20existed%20back%20home%20in%20Shimla.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Himachal%2C%2099%20percent%20of%20the%20homes%20are%20not%20insulated%20and%20rely%20on%20firewood%20and%20electricity%20for%20heating.%20If%20only%20insulation%20were%20used%2C%20we%20could%20stop%20the%20heat%20from%20percolating%20and%20escaping%20outside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20it%20came%20to%20his%20passion%20project%2C%20Sanjay%20decided%20he%20would%20follow%20sensible%20and%20sustainable%20styles%20that%20existed%20the%20world%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20began%20to%20work%20on%20their%20two%20Meena%20Bagh%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20one%20in%20Ratari%20and%20another%20in%20Shimla%2C%20the%20first%20aspect%20that%20Sanjay%20focused%20on%20was%20the%20walls%20that%20held%20the%20structure%20together.%20%E2%80%9CI%20built%20around%20the%20desolate%20walls%20using%20%3Cem%3Ekath%20kuni%3C%2Fem%3E%20architecture.%20It%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%