20story%20of%20the%20city%20and%20how%20it%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20conservation%20architect%20GSV%20Suryanarayana%20Murthy%20to%20The%20Print.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202015%20and%202019%2C%20INTACH%20(Indian%20National%20Trust%20for%20Art%20and%20Cultural%20Heritage)%20published%20a%20report%20stating%20that%20the%20building%20was%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20good%20and%20structurally%20stable%20condition%20and%20did%20not%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20its%20occupants%E2%80%9D.%20In%20November%202019%2C%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Archaeology%20and%20Museums%20and%20the%20Aga%20Khan%20Trust%20for%20Culture%20published%20a%20report%20that%20stated%20that%20the%20heritage%20building%20need%20not%20be%20demolished.%20Both%20reports%20state%20that%20the%20building%20should%20be%20restored%20based%20on%20heritage%20conservation%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTaking%20everything%20into%20consideration%2C%20we%20observed%20that%20the%20heritage%20building%20is%20safe%20for%20another%20century%2C%20however%20it%20requires%20some%20repairs.%20The%20way%20the%20building%20was%20built%20shows%20how%20well%20it%20was%20planned%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20ventilation%2C%20large%20corridors%2C%20and%20proper%20outlets%20for%20the%20water.%20The%20damage%20caused%20to%20it%20is%20purely%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98unscientific%20intervention%E2%80%99.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20park%20opposite%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20people%20to%20relax%2C%20which%20has%20been%20destroyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Anuradha%20Reddy%20of%20INTACH%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20have%20a%20basic%20sense%20of%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306528%2Fshrey-gupta-converts-heritage-bungalow-into-luxury-hotel-nainital-gethia-blue-book-hotels%2F%5C%22%3Eheritage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20an%20idea%20of%20its%20importance.%20These%20are%20mar